1. Stealth was top notch. I will not describe methods used but they were neat and professional lets say that.

2. Once opened the lovely acrid smell filled my car.

3. Appearance was a snow white fluffy fine powder with a slight glisten to it.

4. I tasted product which had not much taste but it tasted the same as it smelt if that makes sense so no extra flavours coming through on the pallet except that distinct coke.

5. No feeling for first 10 mins except a growing numbing sensation which was now all over my mouth. Granted this is also the benzocaine cut.


6. Ten mins in on first small line and a subtle mellow warmth coming.


7. Half a gram down through the nose i feel very high and still not amped up or feeling the jitters.


8. I do feel the need to re dose often but I have been high alot recently and the street cola i had was cut with more stims so it lasted longer ( which is not what i like btw)


9. Gram gone and now feeling content. Two of these would keep me going tgrough the evening.

10. No nasty feeling when the high releases just a subtle relaxed euphoria and a clean nose that feels like normal.
